.TH 2048(1),User Commands,2048(1)

.SH NAME
2048 - sliding tile puzzle game

.SH SYNOPSIS
2048

.SH DESCRIPTION
2048 is an implementation of the classic 4x4 sliding tile puzzle.
Tiles labelled with powers of two are combined by sliding the board in one of four directions;
two tiles with the same value merge into a single tile of twice the value.
A new tile (value 2 or 4) appears after each move that changes the board.
The goal is to create a tile with the value 2048, but play may continue after that.

The current score and the highest tile reached are displayed above the board.

.SH CONTROLS
W or up-arrow: slide up

A or left-arrow: slide left

S or down-arrow: slide down

D or right-arrow: slide right

Q: quit

The game ends when no move can change the board.

.SH EXIT STATUS
2048 exits 0 when the player quits or no moves remain.
